public static final class ArmServiceGrpc.ArmServiceBlockingStub extends io.grpc.stub.AbstractBlockingStub<ArmServiceGrpc.ArmServiceBlockingStub>
A stub to allow clients to do synchronous rpc calls to service ArmService. 
 An ArmService services all arms associated with a robot
